citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 5:50pm on June
28th, 2023. Inspectors rang doorbell at 5:50pm; registrant not present, no responsible adult available. Called contact
number on file and left a message at 5:51pm requesting a return call to coordinate an inspection. Sent text message with
the same request at 6:12pm. No response from registrant within 30 minutes of arrival.
Additional Inspectors:
SARA TOBIAS, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
